OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Freveals cancer diagnosis   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, TV chef James Martin has revealed he   
OL,6, was diagnosed with facial cancer       
OL,7, several years ago.                     
OL,9,FIt follows reports the presenter was   
OL,10,Fasked to change his behaviour at work  
OL,11,Fafter ITV received complaints about his
OL,12,Ftreatment of production staff.         
OL,14,FIn a series of tweets, he described the
OL,15,Fend of 2017 as "one of the most fraught
OL,16,Fand difficult periods of my life".     
OL,18,FHe added he would like to "apologise to
OL,19,Fthe crew involved in this incident, as 
OL,20,FI did at the time."                    
